                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18281023-255-victim1329 t18281023-255-viclabel1484"></join> - he managed my business for some years, and conducted himself well till lately. On the 13th of October Biggs owed me 13l.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18281023-255-person1331">
                  MARGARET 
                  BIGGS
               <interp inst="t18281023-255-person1331" type="surname" value="BIGGS"></interp>
