                     <interp inst="t18281023-255-person1331" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I keep a chandler's-shop, and deal with the prosecutrix. On the <rs id="t18281023-255-cd1485" type="crimeDate">13th of October</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18281023-255-off1483 t18281023-255-cd1485"></join> I owed her 13l. 0s. 1d.; the prisoner came that day, and said."I want some money - my mother has a bill to pay for flour;" I gave him ten sovereigns, and he gave me this receipt - (reads.)</p>
               <p>MRS. EDWARDS. He never returned to me after this; I have not had the money.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18281023-255-person1332">
                  JAMES 
                  HENRY BRYNE
