                     <interp inst="t18281023-255-person1333" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I took the prisoner, and found on him 17s. 4d.; he said that was all, but I found a bag with five sovereigns on him after that.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I think it useless to deny my guilt - I hope judgement will be passed with mercy.</p>
